 875:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_smbus.c **** 
 876:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_smbus.c ****     (#) There is only one mode of transfer:
 877:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_smbus.c ****        (++) Non-Blocking mode : The communication is performed using Interrupts.
